Package: LimROTS
Title: Linear model Reproducibility Optimized Test Statistic
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ali", "Youssef", , "aliali.mostafa99@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5201-387X"))
Description: This function extends the ROTS (Reproducibility Optimized Test Statistic) method by integrating functionality from `limma` for differential expression analysis with optional covariates, survival data, and paired samples. It allows the user to specify additional covariates and models complex experimental designs.
